Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Condense Project Profile hero card and add interactive VR
 avatar

- Remove the campus address, "Tier 1 Award" label, and "2026-2028 EEO IBP
  Grant - Tier 1" eyebrow from the hero card.
- Shrink the program title and the $150,000 funding figure, and roll
  funding into the header row so the card reads as a single, professional
  block.
- Replace the right-hand text column with an animated SVG avatar wearing a
  VR headset. The head pans left-right and tilts up-down on a 7s loop, and
  on hover the avatar tracks the cursor in real time. Motion is suppressed
  for prefers-reduced-motion and the in-app a11y motion toggle.
